*** Add File: README.md
+# Paperclip Onboarding
+
+Local-first onboarding status surface for board/operators running Paperclip onboarding for a new company.
+
+## Current Product Slice
+
+- Shows the current onboarding state.
+- Calls out the next required decision.
+- Identifies the delegated owner.
+- Separates blocker status from raw issue-thread detail.
+
+## Setup
+
+```sh
+npm install
+```
+
+## Run Locally
+
+```sh
+npm run dev
+```
+
+## Verify
+
+```sh
+npm run lint
+npm run test
+npm run build
+```
+
+## Next Product Slice
+
+- Replace the static milestone data with a typed local data source.
+- Add filtering by owner and blocker state once more onboarding tasks exist.
+- Keep Paperclip API integration behind an explicit follow-up once auth and deployment expectations are defined.
